Package: r4subscore
Title: Submission Confidence Index Engine
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", email = "prm@outlook.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7864-5819"))
Description: Converts standardized R4SUB (R for Regulatory Submission) evidence
    into indicator scores, pillar scores, and a Submission Confidence Index
    (SCI). Provides sensitivity analysis, explainability tables, and decision
    band classification to answer the question: are we ready for regulatory
    submission.
